-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/012545_f5577f5435ee3bd5b6274ae161430c17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F012545_f5577f5435ee3bd5b6274ae161430c17.jpg&h=c1a42478&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n靚到畫畫咁<br />\n但睇唔明..."},{"pid":"903a08d06183508cab32cb82c1ed27e6f1bc7b4f","tid":242114,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:44:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實刻意潦草好柒，人哋係寫得快先寫成咁</blockquote><br />\n覺得小學要學寫潦草好反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小學學潦草<br />\n中學比人屌唔好寫<br />\n小學背乘數表<br />\n中學就要人買計算機<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n背成數表係幾有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e7b55b9d39ad1ccdccb605d8230e34fbfb1e35","tid":242114,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:49:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實刻意潦草好柒，人哋係寫得快先寫成咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩咁柒，自小學學左開始到讀完U都係寫潦草<br />\n有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又唔一定寫潦草就會好似copybook咁，<br />\n就算學正階，都係由copybook開始學啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ebd779d46d9c12404f64dc0347a124d722dfa6","tid":242114,"uid":517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實刻意潦草好柒，人哋係寫得快先寫成咁</blockquote>中肯</blockquote><br />\n仲要係Copy book啲寫法，笑死人，除非寫到好似上一輩啲西醫咁就叫有啲Style<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/012545_f5577f5435ee3bd5b6274ae161430c17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F012545_f5577f5435ee3bd5b6274ae161430c17.jpg&h=c1a42478&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n靚到畫畫咁<br />\n但睇唔明...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好提<br />\n我做nurse<br />\n日日都係睇醫生寫呢d字<br />\n開藥落order都係咁 真係睇死人<br />\n真係死人個隻<br />\n好心可唔可以俾少少時間寫<br />\n潦到狂草咁 點睇呀"},{"pid":"fb1ab655f96eb5c2bb4670e2ffce58821af6bfd7","tid":242114,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T20:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實刻意潦草好柒，人哋係寫得快先寫成咁</blockquote>中肯</blockquote><br />\n仲要係Copy book啲寫法，笑死人，除非寫到好似上一輩啲西醫咁就叫有啲Style<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/012545_f5577f5435ee3bd5b6274ae161430c17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F012545_f5577f5435ee3bd5b6274ae161430c17.jpg&h=c1a42478&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n靚到畫畫咁<br />\n但睇唔明...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好提<br />\n我做nurse<br />\n日日都係睇醫生寫呢d字<br />\n開藥落order都係咁 真係睇死人<br />\n真係死人個隻<br />\n好心可唔可以俾少少時間寫<br />\n潦到狂草咁 點睇呀</blockquote><br />\n認同 真係會死人"}]}